Assumption 
	the file name is a unique id for the html doc
_________________________
THE INDEX
_________________________

There is one secodary index,( a hash map) over several primary indices ( default 9 in number )
Eeach priimary index consists of words starting with a limited set of characters.
for eg: every word starting with letter 'a' will be in the same primary index.

PRIMARY INDEX
Every word has document freq. and a postings list consisting of documentId and term freq. pair. 

